result.name: Running Korea

reviews.text: The chicken with fries on pan was very satisfying, seats were comfy, music wasnt too loud, though the hot pot could have served in another way by separate the meat first. Otherwise, it was overall satisfying. Would definitely recommend.
一間不錯的韓國料理而且價錢便宜
價錢親民既韓國餐廳。下午茶只係平午餐幾蚊，所有點了午餐，食物還不錯！泡菜餃子煮得耐得制林晒，但個炸雞熱辣辣配埋甜酸辣汁好好食另外個韓式炒烏冬都炒得好入味，啲烏冬好煙un，但感覺似日式炒烏冬呢🤣恃應們都很有禮貌。泡菜炒飯好辣但好好食😋
食物有質素，食左炸雞塊蜂蜜芥末味，粉不厚很好食，紫菜包飯正常，粉絲有驚喜，粗粉絲軟身好食🖒唯男職員態度一般，但不影響食物質素。***注意下午茶時段由入座起計
芝士鐵板雞好玩，味道一般，芝士越來越少，拉不到絲了

reviews.text: Another LINK shopping centre. There are a few restaurants at the roof with different cuisines.

Excellent indoor market, where one can buy the freshest seafoods. The market features too fruit and vegetable stalls. There are a few small quick eateries on site and a small but good Thai food outlet where one can buy pre prepared Thai dishes.

A small, nice, clean, air-conditioned and well lit wet market with stalls selling fresh vegetables, fruits, meats,  poultry, seafood, ethnic and gourmet foods. There are also few small noodle and desert eateries worth going.
A local shopping mall serving the house estate.
Good for local residents

reviews.text: 品種尚算齊備，衛生程度頗佳。
社區街市，商品價錢亦高。

Another LINK shopping centre. There are a few restaurants at the roof with different cuisines.
大元商場雖屬領展物業，但商場仍保留不少傳統街舖特色。菜市場清潔整齊，人流不少。食肆多元，有韓國、泰國等食店，價錢合理。
